Hey, Rich!

04:44.218 --> 04:45.982
- Rich! Rich!
- Come quick!

04:46.086 --> 04:47.986
- What? ls there something wrong?
- It's a shark!

04:48.088 --> 04:50.056
- The Fonz...
- Fonz got eaten by a shark?!

04:50.157 --> 04:51.852
- He did? Who said that?
- Not me.

04:51.959 --> 04:53.051
What are you
talking about, Rich?

04:53.160 --> 04:54.855
- Well, you just said a shark.
- No, listen.

04:54.962 --> 04:56.930
Fonz is gonna jump over a shark.

04:57.030 --> 04:58.361
Snap out of it, Rich.

04:58.465 --> 05:00.058
