challenged him,

05:07.174 --> 05:09.268
and they're gonna jump
over a shark net.

05:09.376 --> 05:11.811
You get to drive Fonzie.

05:11.912 --> 05:14.574
Shark?! Is he crazy?!

05:17.551 --> 05:20.384
A shark? That is the stupidest
thing I've ever heard.

05:20.487 --> 05:22.922
Stupid, yes. Also dumb.

05:23.023 --> 05:24.354
But it's something I gotta do.

05:24.458 --> 05:27.257
Fonz, y-you're not jumping
over garbage cans on a bike.

05:27.361 --> 05:29.193
You're jumping over a shark.

05:29.296 --> 05:31.390
On nothing. On a couple
of little skis.

05:31.498 --> 05:34.263
One little slip
and chomp, chomp, chomp.

05:34.368 --> 05:36.268
Thanks a lot for your support.

05:36.370 --> 05:38.429
Look, I was challenged.

05:38.538 --> 05:39.630
I gotta jump-.

05:39.740 --> 05:41.299
Challenged?!
The guy's bluffing.

05:41.408 --> 05:43.308
He's not gonna jump
over some shark.

05:43.410 --> 05:44.900
That's right.
He was bluffing. Huh?

05:45.012 --> 05:46.241
All right,
let me tell you something,

05:46.346 --> 05:47.575
that's another reason
I got to jump.

05:47.681 --> 05:49.911
'Cause that punk is trying
to take a free ride.

05:50.017 --> 05:51.451
Look, you already tied him

05:51.551 --> 05:53.383
and-and his championship
patches.

05:53.487 --> 05:55.717
So why can't you just drop it?

05:55.822 --> 05:57.722
I have to meet his bluff.

05:57.824 --> 06:01.385
I ain't going back to Milwaukee
a double failure.

06:01.495 --> 06:03.486
Now, are you coming?

06:04.498 --> 06:06.933
Let's go.

06:08.702 --> 06:11.194
Girls.

06:11.305 --> 06:13.865
So, Prince Valiant,
are you ready?

06:13.974 --> 06:16.671
(chuckles)
Are you actually gonna do it?

06:16.777 --> 06:19.041
- Yeah. Are you?
- Yeah.

06:19.146 --> 06:22.912
Well, look, since you had
a condition on this tiebreaker,

06:23.016 --> 06:24.780
I got one, too.

06:24.885 --> 06:26.250
Go ahead.

06:26.353 --> 06:29.050
You go first.

06:29.156 --> 06:30.715
That way,
when you jump and fall,

06:30.824 --> 06:33.384
that little shark ain't gonna be
so hungry when I go.

06:33.493 --> 06:34.517
(girls laugh)

06:34.628 --> 06:37.529
Well, I...

06:37.631 --> 06:39.861
(clucking like a chicken)

06:39.967 --> 06:42.197
-(laughter)
- Yeah, all right!

06:42.302 --> 06:43.792
Wait a minute, kid,
you know, he's...

06:43.904 --> 06:44.996
Shut up!

06:45.105 --> 06:46.937
Fire up the boat.

06:47.040 --> 06:48.337
I'm jumping the shark.

06:48.442 --> 06:51.173
Gosh, I'm always
firing up a boat.

06:51.278 --> 06:53.269
(indistinct chatter, cooing)

07:07.027 --> 07:08.586
Oh, I can't watch.

07:08.695 --> 07:10.254
What if he doesn't make it?

07:10.364 --> 07:13.527
Relax. How much can one shark
eat anyway, huh?

07:13.633 --> 07:16.864
I'm kidding. I'm nervous, too.

07:16.970 --> 07:19.337
Oh, Mom, Dad, over here!

07:21.908 --> 07:23.740
Where have you guys been?

07:23.844 --> 07:25.141
There, now, you see?

07:25.245 --> 07:27.077
You and your
"just one more ashtray, Howard."

07:27.180 --> 07:28.341
Now we missed the race.

07:28.448 --> 07:30.542
But we may never get
to Hollywood again.

07:30.650 --> 07:33.051
We won't have to. We're gonna
have half of it in Milwaukee.

07:33.153 --> 07:35.383
Oh, sit on it, Howard.

07:35.489 --> 07:38.220
Forget the souvenirs.
You've got to stop Fonzie.

07:38.325 --> 07:39.759
I thought the race was over.

07:39.860 --> 07:41.055
No, it was a tie.

07:41.161 --> 07:42.390
Well, what's all the excitement?

07:42.496 --> 07:45.227
The Fonz and the California Kid
are gonna break the tie.

07:45.332 --> 07:47.300
They're gonna jump over a shark!

07:47.401 --> 07:50.462
- Isn't that dangerous?
- Well, of course it's dangerous.

07:50.570 --> 07:51.594
Well, you should stop them.

07:51.705 --> 07:53.104
- We've got to do something.
- Yeah!

07:53.206 --> 07:55.573
Well, what would you like me
to do, talk to the shark?

07:55.675 --> 07:56.665
Oh, Howard, would you?

07:56.777 --> 07:59.144
No, Marion, I wouldn't.

08:07.521 --> 08:09.421
This is ridiculous.

08:24.271 --> 08:27.036
(indistinct chatter)

08:59.940 --> 09:01.465
The California Kid quit!

09:01.575 --> 09:03.009
-(all shouting)
- ALL: Chicken!

09:03.110 --> 09:05.511
Good! Now Fonzie doesn't have
to do the jump.

09:05.612 --> 09:07.706
- Boy, that was close.
- You did it, Fonz.

09:07.814 --> 09:09.373
- Winner and still champion.
- Yeah.

09:09.483 --> 09:10.382
All right, it's my turn.

09:10.484 --> 09:11.974
Come on, row me
out to the ski boat.

09:12.085 --> 09:13.211
Get in the boat?!

09:13.320 --> 09:15.049
Fonz, you don't have
to jump now.

09:15.155 --> 09:16.645
The California Kid quit.

09:16.756 --> 09:18.315
The Fonz don't quit.

09:18.425 --> 09:20.587
Are you gonna drive
for me or not?

09:21.962 --> 09:23.191
No.

09:23.296 --> 09:24.593
Malph, get in the boat
and drive.

09:24.698 --> 09:26.029
All right, Fonz.

09:26.133 --> 09:27.328
You won't be sorry.

09:27.434 --> 09:28.765
This time I'll remember
to untie it.

09:28.869 --> 09:29.768
All right! Okay!

09:29.870 --> 09:31.565
I'm gonna drive.

09:31.671 --> 09:34.606
What is this,
more of the Fonzarelli Code?

09:34.708 --> 09:36.005
You don't understand,
Cunningham.

09:36.109 --> 09:38.134
