13:22.335 --> 13:24.531
I mean, he's got
the best boat money can buy,

13:24.637 --> 13:26.833
he's got custom skis,
he's got a Porsche.

13:26.940 --> 13:28.237
Yeah, he does, he does.

13:28.341 --> 13:30.537
