yours and mine, <i>Happy</i> Days! ♪

24:32.638 --> 24:35.005
♪ Good-bye, gray sky,
hello, blue ♪

24:35.107 --> 24:37.508
♪ There's nothing can hold me
when I hold you ♪

24:37.610 --> 24:40.045
♪ It feels so right,
it can't be wrong ♪

